<button onclick="playback()">Play</button>
<button onclick="reset()">Rewind</button>
<button onclick="clearSong()">Delete Recording</button><br>
  You must rewind to play your song again.<br>
  Recording starts automatically.<br>
  Playback will not pause recording.<br>
  Deleting recording will start new recording.<br>
  Current issues: Sometimes notes will stop playing due to lag; you will have to wait or refresh to fix.
</div>
